@startuml SH-MP-EG Gateway Component
title SH-MP-EG Edge Gateway — Component View

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "Perception Layer" as P {
  component "ESP32-S3 Node\n(Wi-Fi, DHT22, Buzzer)" as ESP
  component "STM32F103 Node\n(BLE, LDR, LED)" as STM
}

package "Edge Gateway (Raspberry Pi 4B)" as G {
  component "wifi_receiver\n(Flask + asyncio TCP)" as Wifi
  component "ble_receiver\n(bleak GATT)" as Ble
  component "data_converter\n(unified JSON + schema)" as Conv
  component "mqtt_publisher\n(paho-mqtt)" as Mqtt
  database "MessageCache\n(SQLite)" as Cache
}

package "Network Layer" as N {
  component "EMQX Broker\n(docker)" as Emqx
}

package "Application Layer" as A {
  component "Node-RED\nRule Engine" as NodeRed
  component "Web UI" as UI
}

ESP --> Wifi : HTTP / TCP JSON
STM --> Ble  : BLE Notification
Wifi --> Conv
Ble  --> Conv
Conv --> Mqtt
Mqtt <--> Cache : offline buffering
Mqtt --> Emqx   : publish telemetry
Emqx --> NodeRed: subscribe
NodeRed --> Emqx: publish command
Emqx --> Mqtt   : command
Mqtt --> Ble    : on_command -> BLE write
UI --> Emqx     : MQTT over WS / HTTP

@enduml


@startuml SH-MP-EG Sequence — Rule Trigger
title Rule trigger: high temperature -> buzzer

actor "ESP32-S3" as ESP
participant "wifi_receiver" as WR
participant "data_converter" as DC
participant "mqtt_publisher" as MP
participant "EMQX" as B
participant "Node-RED" as NR
participant "(Buzzer)" as BUZ

ESP -> WR: POST /api/v1/telemetry\n{id,t=30,h,l}
WR -> DC: normalize_wifi(raw)
DC --> WR: unified JSON
WR -> MP: publish_unified(msg)
MP -> B: smarthome/v1/telemetry/wifi/<id>
B -> NR: deliver
NR -> NR: switch payload.temperature > 28 ?
NR -> B: smarthome/v1/command/wifi/<id>\n{buzzer:true}
B -> MP: deliver command
MP -> WR: on_command('wifi', id, {...})
note right: (当前实现未对\nWi-Fi 做下行写入；\n可扩展为 TCP 长连接)

@enduml
